"     Deputy Editor",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?29/57/30615/contributors\">",
"     Geraldine Finlay, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
